item.title: At an AWS Event...
item.description: To complete this workshop, you are provided with an AWS account via the AWS Event Engine service. A team hash will be provided to you by event staff. If you are currently logged in to an AWS Account, you can logout using this link Create AWS Account 1 . Connect to the portal by clicking the button or browsing to https://dashboard.eventengine.run/. The following screen shows up. Enter the provided hash in the text box.
